# Vercel Deployment

- **Build Command**: Set to `npm run build` in Vercel Settings.
  - This ensures `postbuild` (migrations) runs automatically.
  - Do NOT set to `next build --webpack` directly.
- **Build Script**: `package.json` should have `"build": "next build --webpack"` if Turbopack fails.
